Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.69,0:00:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.34,0:01:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次，一定要成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.70,0:02:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也知道用时光机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.58,0:02:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,穿越时空是犯罪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.17,0:02:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是，身为一个科学家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想尝试制造出不可能的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.05,0:02:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未来的我能制造出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.17,0:02:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在的我也一定可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.59,0:02:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.39,0:02:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？又失败？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.89,0:02:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么就是启动不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.65,0:02:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道说这个物品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.36,0:02:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是未来才有的物质吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行，不能因为这点事就放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.99,0:02:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定有能代替的物质的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.29,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「出来吧神龙！谁能实现愿望！？」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.52,0:02:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？你说让我们复活？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.89,0:03:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,认真想了下，我总是把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,界王大人的事排在后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.09,0:03:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且，上次叫神龙出来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.14,0:03:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只问了超级龙珠的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以，我想龙珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.27,0:03:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也应该可以使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.82,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到，能从你口中说出那么温柔的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.11,0:03:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然，你有把我放在心上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.93,0:03:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,界王大人…呼吸…不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉，抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.92,0:03:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,水…水…水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话是这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.30,0:03:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会又在最后关头说还是下次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.35,0:03:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次你放心，相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.87,0:04:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有了这个物质，时光机就能完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我看看…在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.50,0:04:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地底下？而且还是那么深的地下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.34,0:04:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？孙君！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂，孙君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然进入别人的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.72,0:04:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连门都不敲，想干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.81,0:04:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算你这么说…瞬间移动无法敲门啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了，你这人就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后呢，什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能不能把龙珠雷达借我啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？龙珠雷达？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.44,0:04:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢啦，布玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你叫神龙出来是要许什么愿望啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.53,0:04:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想让界王大人复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，我借走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吓死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是被孙君知道我在制造时光机的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.88,0:05:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,绝对会传到比鲁斯那里去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.43,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对喔！刚才的物质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向神龙许愿不就可以了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真枯燥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.11,0:05:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪里才有朝气勃勃的女孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,买新裙子啦～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要跑太快，很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.96,0:05:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然，有女孩子在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.08,0:05:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以买可爱的服装，买东西也开心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧？18号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？怎么啦？18号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说起来，克林他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.97,0:05:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从来没有说过想要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是他会买各种东西给玛伦和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.90,0:05:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他想要的东西到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.89,0:06:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偶尔，我也想买个礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给他一个惊喜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,18号真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.87,0:06:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布玛小姐，午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.17,0:06:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人，你来这干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.34,0:06:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「来这干嘛」？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们想请你带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们去吃美食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.97,0:06:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美食？对喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.51,0:06:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真是问了个蠢问题呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.68,0:06:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然是这样呢，来找好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危险，危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.77,0:06:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差点就自己说出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过，这两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.98,0:06:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偏偏挑这个时候来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.11,0:06:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然这样，就快点带他们去吃完美食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.45,0:06:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在悟空回来之前，打发他们走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.79,0:07:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出来啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快看！这次是那么柔软有弹性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.55,0:07:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,维斯，你看，爪子在动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.47,0:07:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能不能别玩，快点吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好，7个集齐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.35,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂，布玛～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.23,0:07:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.12,0:07:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好，开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.45,0:07:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出来吧，神龙！实现我的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.64,0:08:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉！我想起有些事要先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.74,0:08:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们请慢用！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么多！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头的挖不出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人，在这时候就要用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.37,0:08:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蟹甲壳类大腿步足身体掏肉工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说啥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.88,0:08:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是说，蟹甲壳类大腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.75,0:08:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说吧，把愿望说出来，什么都能实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.34,0:08:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前实现了1个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还剩下2个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.48,0:08:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说吧，第1个愿望是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.07,0:08:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于能复活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.86,0:08:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，把界王大人的星球上的3人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.39,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,禁止插队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.13,0:09:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还什么都没许愿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.21,0:09:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要先警告你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.05,0:09:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你有前科
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我女孩子的内裤！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空，是你叫出来的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要许什么愿啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想让界王大人复活呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.62,0:09:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是这个吗？那还剩1个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能不能给我实现愿望？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，是给我实现愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.62,0:09:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的愿望？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.21,0:09:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正，肯定又是要什么朝气勃勃的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.04,0:09:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么叫「又是」？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.13,0:09:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空你能明白吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.67,0:09:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作为妻子也有想要实现的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.30,0:10:01.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不，给时日不多的老人许个愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.93,0:10:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听听我的愿望！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可耻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.48,0:10:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不能许愿吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.40,0:10:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,征服世界的愿望终于要实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.49,0:10:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至今为止，我们在这里忍受着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.04,0:10:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,寄人篱下的生活，全是为了这一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.58,0:10:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是为了每天能吃到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.58,0:10:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美味的饭菜吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确实也有这原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.67,0:10:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.76,0:10:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们俩把这感动的瞬间烙印在眼里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皮拉夫大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯，悟天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.03,0:11:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看见神龙出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.57,0:11:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,许愿了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.57,0:11:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还没呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么就实现我们的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们的愿望？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.88,0:11:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为，实现愿望的总是你们大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.71,0:11:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,偶尔也让我们许愿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.76,0:11:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧？悟天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.88,0:11:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行，小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.63,0:11:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小小年纪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只想着许愿就能实现一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这教育不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.39,0:11:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,18号说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,年轻要多吃点苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.15,0:11:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,18号阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行就是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.13,0:11:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都叫你不许插队！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好辛苦…好辛苦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道啦，放手…老爷爷！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.66,0:11:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁都行，快说出第1个愿望！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.26,0:12:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加油！使劲！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.65,0:12:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还差一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皮拉夫大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事吧，皮拉夫大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.94,0:12:22.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚刚是我大意了，这次一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.27,0:12:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.24,0:12:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皮拉夫大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有剩下的愿望吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.00,0:12:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.46,0:12:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实，阿包从早上开始就高烧不退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.21,0:12:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿包吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这太糟糕了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也去了医院给她开药了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.72,0:12:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知是否因为赛亚人的血统，全都不起作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.64,0:12:55.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以，我想向神龙许愿，把阿包治好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还用问，当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点治好她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.61,0:13:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.65,0:13:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.24,0:13:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙，请让阿包恢复精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太简单了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿包！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.05,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恢复了吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.27,0:13:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.14,0:13:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愿望实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了，悟饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.82,0:13:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是！非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.49,0:13:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比迪丽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.78,0:13:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来吧，说出最后一个愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后一个？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.62,0:14:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚刚用了一个，现在就只剩一个愿望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.08,0:14:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉啦，为了阿包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.75,0:14:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，武天老师爷爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.88,0:14:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们的愿望就等下次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.72,0:14:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.07,0:14:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，我让界王大人复活啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你了，悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂，神龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.94,0:14:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把界王大人行星上的3人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,界王大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.40,0:14:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么一定要这次复活呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错，18号说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.16,0:14:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,界王大人等下次也行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们这群人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…我先约好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只是口头约定而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.63,0:14:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,界王大人才没当真呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.84,0:14:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说不定，死了才轻松呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.84,0:14:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不如给我许愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.55,0:14:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都说了，这次轮到我们啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们这群人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,界王大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.22,0:14:57.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都在自话自说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空是为了让我复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.77,0:15:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才去收集龙珠的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次我绝不退让！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.94,0:15:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么那么执着要复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活着和死了不都一样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.53,0:15:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心情不一样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.36,0:15:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「心情」？那还不如给我许愿！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.01,0:15:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我活着就是为了朝气勃勃的女孩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.87,0:15:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是给我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.04,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来还要花很长时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.01,0:15:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶…一次两次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.68,0:15:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,皮拉夫大人，要不…我们还是放弃吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.22,0:15:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,肯定是今天运气不好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.05,0:15:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住嘴！我怎么可能就这样善罢罢休！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.52,0:15:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.94,0:15:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.65,0:15:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我等等！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这次就让给你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布玛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.20,0:16:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙还在的话，就是说还有剩下的愿望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个愿望，归我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且，要不是因为有我的龙珠雷达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.34,0:16:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们能叫得出神龙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太狡猾了，明明最后才来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是！我想要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克林到底想要什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傻瓜，18号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克林的回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用问，你我都很清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.27,0:16:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「我只要18号还有玛伦在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其他什么都可以不要」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.23,0:16:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克林的话，绝对会这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.24,0:16:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.24,0:16:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确实是…他会说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.33,0:16:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以，你快点回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.42,0:16:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟他一起才是最好的礼物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的愿望呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.67,0:16:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝气勃勃的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.34,0:16:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给1千万钱币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.51,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫4-5个朝气勃勃的女孩过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.52,0:17:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太厉害了布玛，神龙都要甘拜下风了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.96,0:17:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布玛，我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女孩子的内裤是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.16,0:17:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？不不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.95,0:17:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,18号，帮我揍飞这个变态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.37,0:17:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听我说到最后！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.59,0:17:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特兰克斯和悟天呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们的愿望？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.42,0:17:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.42,0:17:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有的话就实现不了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.84,0:17:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶，可是我很想试试啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么，首先就得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.39,0:17:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到想要实现的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那应该会比这要困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.44,0:17:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下，大家的问题都解决了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.82,0:17:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的愿望还没实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么，你还没许愿吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发生了很多事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么…就这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你去地底的深处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帮我把这个物质取出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.25,0:18:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之后，你就能实现你的愿望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.75,0:18:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地底的深处？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.39,0:18:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去那里的话，我会不会死掉啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.13,0:18:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有我制造的特殊套装，就没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉，你们没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.31,0:18:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.68,0:18:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么关系嘛！多等一会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗，那好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.11,0:18:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就向比鲁斯大人说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙欺负人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.24,0:18:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么…就再等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.42,0:18:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…孙君，拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.51,0:18:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靠你了，悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.60,0:19:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,满足，满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.55,0:19:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们走吧，比鲁斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老板，味道真不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是吃得有点麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说起来，布玛小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然是要干嘛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.65,0:19:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,中途就跑掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙那家伙，居然还在？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.61,0:19:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊呀，悟空的气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.25,0:19:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是这个吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.75,0:19:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.04,0:19:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在这地方干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.64,0:19:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那个…还没好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.23,0:19:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但…但是…身体要消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.07,0:20:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人他们也一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.11,0:20:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比…比鲁斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没…没想到还能见到您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.79,0:20:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你干嘛在发抖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.08,0:20:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在…等着他们许愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.02,0:20:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.95,0:20:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙君，孙君！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你的东西拿回来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.67,0:20:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉…那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个东西，是指这个吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.26,0:20:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特意叫悟空去取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.06,0:20:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个东西，你要来干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.27,0:20:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会是…在制造时光机吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.44,0:20:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,穿越时空是重罪，我告诉过你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.32,0:20:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？啊…不…不是这样的…那个…这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.28,0:20:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常抱歉！我再也不做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那，这个也不需要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的时光机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.84,0:21:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空！快许愿！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.18,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，糟了，差点忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.10,0:21:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神龙！把界王大人的星球上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.47,0:21:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,极限了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.99,0:21:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉，界王大人…没赶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.60,0:21:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢…蠢…你这蠢货！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.20,0:21:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是早就叫你说的吗！
